<p>
  Bob is warp's 32k game compo entry for
  <a href="http://ms.demo.org">Mekka &amp; Symposium</a>
  2001, it got 7th place.
</p>

<p>
  Bob is a 2 player pc re-implementation of a classic 
  c64 game called jawbreaker. It was coded by warp in C on an
  old pentium 133MHZ, the code is a lot cleaner and better
  optimized compared to 8bit :).
</p>

<p class="screenshot">
