  The music was made by tharsis and the player is a hybrid of
  fxmp-0.0.21 and fxmp-0.0.22-pre2 with some size optimizations.
  <a href="http://flare.theplanes.org">fxmp</a> by spectre
  of <a href="http://flare.theplanes.org">flare</a>.
</p>

<p>
  Linux/GGI port was mostly done by smoke of
  <a href="http://die.die.ms/ecfh">ecfh</a>.
</p>

<p>
